{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:0","text":"Materials 控制对象的外观，而 pattern 节点通过在表面上改变材质 Bxdf 的参数来控制细节。这类似于纹理艺术家使用纹理来控制材质外观的方式。RenderMan 随附一组 pattern 节点，可用于纹理化、颜色校正、凹凸处理以及各种实用着色系统。"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:1","text":"这些 pattern 节点可分为以下类别："}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:2","text":"Image Texture（图像纹理）"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:3","text":"使用纹理图像驱动 pattern。"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:4","text":"PxrMultiTexture"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:5","text":"PxrProjectionLayer"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:6","text":"PxrPtexture"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:8","text":"Procedural Texture（程序化纹理）"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:9","text":"以程序方式创建 noise（噪声）和 pattern。"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:10","text":"PxrChecker"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:11","text":"PxrCurvature"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:12","text":"PxrFractal"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:13","text":"PxrVoronoise"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:14","text":"PxrWorley"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:15","text":"PxrPhasorNoise"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:16","text":"Manifolds（映射流形）"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:17","text":"Manifolds 会告诉渲染器如何在表面上应用 pattern。这会控制重复、放置和尺寸等特征。"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:18","text":"PxrManifold2D"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:19","text":"PxrBumpManifold2D"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:20","text":"PxrManifold3D"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:21","text":"PxrProjector"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:22","text":"PxrRandomTextureManifold"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:23","text":"PxrRoundCube"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:24","text":"PxrTileManifold"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:25","text":"PxrHexTileManifold"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:26","text":"Color（颜色）"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:27","text":"在 shading network 中创建或修改颜色。"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:28","text":"PxrBlackBody"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:29","text":"PxrBlend"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:30","text":"PxrClamp"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:31","text":"PxrColorCorrect"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:32","text":"PxrColorSpace"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:33","text":"PxrExposure"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:34","text":"PxrGamma"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:36","text":"PxrHSL"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:37","text":"PxrInvert"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:38","text":"PxrLayeredBlend"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:39","text":"PxrMix"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:40","text":"PxrProjectionStack"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:41","text":"PxrRamp"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:42","text":"PxrRemap"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:43","text":"PxrThinFilm"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:44","text":"PxrThreshold"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:45","text":"PxrVary"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:46","text":"Bump（凹凸）"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:47","text":"创建低幅度的浮雕效果。"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:48","text":"PxrBump"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:49","text":"PxrBumpMixer"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:50","text":"PxrNormalMap"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:51","text":"PxrFlakes"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:52","text":"aaOceanPrmanShader"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:53","text":"Geometry Nodes（几何节点）"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:54","text":"可以使用这些节点计算几何属性和向量。"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:55","text":"PxrDirt"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:59","text":"PxrDot"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:60","text":"PxrCross"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:61","text":"PxrFacingRatio"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:62","text":"PxrTangentField"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:63","text":"Script（脚本）"}
{"id":"16eadb67c73036050c32d8ae0da4ddb676c856f047ee2bfa318e741f0c89beb5","text":"OSL Patterns"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:65","text":"Utility（实用工具）"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:66","text":"PxrAttribute"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:67","text":"PxrMatteID"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:68","text":"PxrPrimvar"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:69","text":"PxrVariable"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:70","text":"PxrToFloat"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:71","text":"PxrToFloat3"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:72","text":"PxrTee"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:73","text":"PxrShadedSide"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:74","text":"Baking（烘焙）"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:75","text":"这些直通 pattern 旨在允许用户烘焙任意 pattern 网络。"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:76","text":"PxrBakeTexture"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:77","text":"PxrBakePointCloud"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:78","text":"Guidance for Writing Your Own Patterns（编写自定义 Patterns 指南）"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:79","text":"你不必局限于 RenderMan 提供的 pattern。如果遵循"}
{"item_id":"a4a6a36ec6:81","text":"中的指导，就可以构建自己的 pattern。XPU 只运行 OSL patterns，而 RIS 同时运行 C++ 和 OSL patterns。"}
